{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Worthing{\*\xmlclose}. And }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5316996\charrsid3239883 he\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
